# Duel Masters Rules Source Of Truth

For all work in this project, treat `Duel_Masters_rules.md` as the authoritative rules reference.

- Read and follow `Duel_Masters_rules.md` before making gameplay, rules engine, card effect parsing, validation, test, or data-model changes.
- Ensure all coding decisions that affect Duel Masters behavior are aligned with `Duel_Masters_rules.md`.
- If implementation details conflict with `Duel_Masters_rules.md`, prefer the document and call out the mismatch before changing behavior.
- Do not invent Duel Masters rule behavior from memory when the rule document can answer it.
